ApproxsimClient.timeline
Class TimelineActivityPanel

java.lang.Object
  java.awt.Component
      java.awt.Container
          javax.swing.JComponent
              javax.swing.JPanel
                  ApproxsimClient.timeline.TimelineCanvasPanel
                      ApproxsimClient.timeline.TimelineActivityPanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
DragGestureListener, MouseListener, MouseMotionListener, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, Serializable, EventListener, Accessible, javax.media.opengl.GLEventListener
public class TimelineActivityPanel
extends TimelineCanvasPanel
implements DragGestureListener

This panel displays the activities in the timeline. Each activity is represented with it's identifier, the start and end times, the resource, the affiliation and the symbol with two arrows (at the start and end times). Both the symbol and the arrows are DnD enabled.
